Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡骨大夫  你想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  快救救那孩子
